<h1 style="color:blue;font-style:bold;font-family:algerian;font-size:60px;text-decoration:underline">
<center>AUTOBIOGRAPHY OF A SMARTPHONE </center> 
<h1>
     

       <p align="justify" style= "color:orange;font-family:Edwardian Script ITC;font-size:40px">I am a smartphone.I was manufactured in a factory of Samsung in Rajasthan.Then I was transported to kolkata.It was a very streneous journey for me coz there were almost 1000 smarphones with me.It took 1 week to reach kolkata.I was displayed in a dealer shop of samsung brand.I was black in color,with quad rear camera and dual front cameras. <br></p>



   <p align="justify" style="color:white;font-family:Edwardian Script ITC;font-size:40px"> 
   Due to this growing technology and nowdays smartphone has became an essential thing in human life,without phone they cannot do their studies also,so it took only 2 days to sale me.I was bought by a person for his child's studies.As I was expensive he always took care of me.When the usage of mine is completed the child kept me in right place.He played games in me which I also enjoyed.One day I slipped from the hands of the child and fell on the floor,I was hurt a little bit only my screen cracked.As I was in warranty period it did not cost for repairing me. After 2 yrs the child became bored on me,so he started neglecting me.He did not keep me in my right place.He downloaded many games on me and I frequently got hanged as I was overloaded.One day as I got hanged for a long time he threw me so badly that I was almost dead.He did not repair me as I was not in warranty period and have to pay a lot of money.As I was injured a lot I started malfunnctioning.<br></p> 


    <p align="justify" style="color:green;font-family:Edwardian Script ITC;font-size:40px">
    He did not repair me instead threw me in a dustbin.Now I am in the dustbin,no one cared about me as I am a non-living thing and I cannot  expresss my feelings out like all humans do.<br></p><hr>


